title: Freescale Semiconductor to Announce Third Quarter Earnings on Oct. 22, 2015
text:
Companies mentioned in this article: Freescale Semiconductor, Ltd. 
AUSTIN, Texas -- (BUSINESS WIRE) -- Freescale Semiconductor, Ltd. (NYSE:FSL) will announce its third quarter 2015 financial results in a press release at 3:15 p.m. Central Time, on Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. The press release will be posted at www.freescale.com/investor . 
The company does not plan to host an earnings conference call and will offer limited guidance for the fourth quarter of 2015 due to the pending merger with NXP Semiconductors. 
About Freescale Semiconductor 
Freescale Semiconductor (NYSE:FSL) enables secure, embedded processing solutions for the Internet of Tomorrow. Freescale’s solutions drive a more innovative and connected world, simplifying our lives and making us safer. While serving the world’s largest companies, Freescale is also committed to supporting science, technology, engineering and math (STEM) education, enabling the next generation of innovators. www.freescale.com
